sentence: Wednesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 7,295.24.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 2.07 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 1.08 to 1 ratio.
There were 1531 advancers and 1413 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 56 stocks reached a 52 week high and 16 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up .25% for the day; a total of 16.84 points.
Applied Materials, Inc. ( AMAT ) had the largest percent change down (-5.41%) while Intuitive Surgical, Inc. ( ISRG ) had the largest percent change gain rising 8.17%.
The Dow Jones index closed down -.16% for the day; a total of -38.56 points.

The current value is 24,748.07. International Business Machines Corporation ( IBM ) had the largest percent change down (-7.53%) while Home Depot, Inc. (The) ( HD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 2.82%.
